title: Looking for a Jungler for my ranked team (Plat V Minimum please)
body: Hi guys,, my team which is currently gold v but has a plat/diamond active roster is looking for a jungler to play for us as our jungler cannot play as much anymore, I'd really prefer you to be platinum or above and active is definitely a must as we practice quite often, please leave your IGN below and i'll add you in game. Thanks!

replies.body: Yo dude add me in game 'Phil Collins'
